## 2026-04-04 - Set switcher renders all sets flat with no folder grouping
- Added `buildFolderGroups` helper that groups flat set names by their first path segment (e.g. `brand/colors` + `brand/spacing` → a "brand/" folder group). Preserves original order.
- Modified `SwitchView` to render collapsible folder groups when any set name contains a `/`. Folder headers show a chevron toggle + item count + active-set dot indicator when collapsed.
- Items inside a folder are indented (`pl-6`) and show only the sub-path (after the first `/`). Ungrouped sets render flat as before.

